---
title: Valentine's Salmon en Croûte with Spinach Salad in Caper Vinaigrette
description: Salmon fillets encased in a puff pastry shell that's brimming with spinach and cream cheese is more than enough to impress your Valentine. The spinach salad with sweet bell pepper and a caper vinaigrette provides the perfect zesty balance.
